  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071390/extras/10b6427b7d8360e0dc29031320eb1393.poster.avif?t=1753489242\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071390/extras/10b6427b7d8360e0dc29031320eb1393.webm?t=1753489242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071390/extras/10b6427b7d8360e0dc29031320eb1393.mp4?t=1753489242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Chess: The Lost Pieces</strong></h2><br>The chess game with deck building. Use unique pieces such as,<br>- a pawn that needs to be <i>charged to move</i>,<br>- a rook that can <i>pull pieces from afar</i>, <br>- a knight that gets more mobile <i>the longer it stays on the board</i>, <br>- a bishop that moves off the board and ends up on the other side, <br>- a queen that <i>captures its capturer when it get gets captured</i>, or <br>- a king that can<i> swap places with its queen</i> or queen class piece!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071390/extras/1c5e804ddf40d5af5d8590fa840c38e6.poster.avif?t=1753489242\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071390/extras/1c5e804ddf40d5af5d8590fa840c38e6.webm?t=1753489242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071390/extras/1c5e804ddf40d5af5d8590fa840c38e6.mp4?t=1753489242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Roguelike Chess<br>- Start with a rook, a knight and a bishop, build a full army deck as you go!<br>- Progress through the map, recruit new pieces and beat ppponents!<br>- Use bottled pieces to get a material advantage!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071390/extras/a6ef2a8b0cfb9f85f9edd6151d52c003.poster.avif?t=1753489242\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071390/extras/a6ef2a8b0cfb9f85f9edd6151d52c003.webm?t=1753489242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071390/extras/a6ef2a8b0cfb9f85f9edd6151d52c003.mp4?t=1753489242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features:<br>- Use <strong>30+ new and unique chess pieces</strong> to defeat opponents<br>- Make your <strong>own chess piece deck</strong>, and battle against friends or strangers<br>- A <strong>randomised roguelike story mode</strong> to unlock even more pieces<br>- <strong>30 puzzles</strong> with the new pieces to sharpen your skills<br>- ...and Online Play so you can get get beaten by your friends!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071390/extras/a47ed4467fe1063def1ebd25d6ea911b.poster.avif?t=1753489242\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071390/extras/a47ed4467fe1063def1ebd25d6ea911b.webm?t=1753489242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071390/extras/a47ed4467fe1063def1ebd25d6ea911b.mp4?t=1753489242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071390/extras/10b6427b7d8360e0dc29031320eb1393.poster.avif?t=1753489242\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071390/extras/10b6427b7d8360e0dc29031320eb1393.webm?t=1753489242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071390/extras/10b6427b7d8360e0dc29031320eb1393.mp4?t=1753489242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Chess: The Lost Pieces</strong></h2><br>The chess game with deck building. Use unique pieces such as,<br>- a pawn that needs to be <i>charged to move</i>,<br>- a rook that can <i>pull pieces from afar</i>, <br>- a knight that gets more mobile <i>the longer it stays on the board</i>, <br>- a bishop that moves off the board and ends up on the other side, <br>- a queen that <i>captures its capturer when it get gets captured</i>, or <br>- a king that can<i> swap places with its queen</i> or queen class piece!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071390/extras/1c5e804ddf40d5af5d8590fa840c38e6.poster.avif?t=1753489242\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071390/extras/1c5e804ddf40d5af5d8590fa840c38e6.webm?t=1753489242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071390/extras/1c5e804ddf40d5af5d8590fa840c38e6.mp4?t=1753489242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Roguelike Chess<br>- Start with a rook, a knight and a bishop, build a full army deck as you go!<br>- Progress through the map, recruit new pieces and beat ppponents!<br>- Use bottled pieces to get a material advantage!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071390/extras/a6ef2a8b0cfb9f85f9edd6151d52c003.poster.avif?t=1753489242\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071390/extras/a6ef2a8b0cfb9f85f9edd6151d52c003.webm?t=1753489242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071390/extras/a6ef2a8b0cfb9f85f9edd6151d52c003.mp4?t=1753489242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Features:<br>- Use <strong>30+ new and unique chess pieces</strong> to defeat opponents<br>- Make your <strong>own chess piece deck</strong>, and battle against friends or strangers<br>- A <strong>randomised roguelike story mode</strong> to unlock even more pieces<br>- <strong>30 puzzles</strong> with the new pieces to sharpen your skills<br>- ...and Online Play so you can get get beaten by your friends!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071390/extras/a47ed4467fe1063def1ebd25d6ea911b.poster.avif?t=1753489242\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071390/extras/a47ed4467fe1063def1ebd25d6ea911b.webm?t=1753489242\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2071390/extras/a47ed4467fe1063def1ebd25d6ea911b.mp4?t=1753489242\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
